#: original_texis/windows.texi:1337
msgid "Note that this argument does not have the same meaning as in other functions which scan all live windows (@pxref{Cyclic Window Ordering}).  Specifically, the meanings of @code{t} and @code{nil} here are the opposite of what they are in those other functions."
msgstr "この引数の意味は、すべての生きたウィンドウを走査する他の関数(@ref{Cyclic Window Ordering}を参照)の場合とは異なることに注意。特にここでの@code{t}と@code{nil}のもつ意味は、これら他の関数の場合とは逆になる。"

#. type: cindex
#: original_texis/windows.texi:1342
#, no-wrap
msgid "recombining windows"
msgstr "recombining windows"

